<div class="about-content rte">
  {%- if page.content != blank -%}
    {{ page.content }}
  {%- else -%}
    <h2>From our home to yours</h2>
    <p>Molly &amp; Sophie isn't a faceless big-box pet store — it's a small, family-run shop run from a cozy house with three goofy dogs underfoot. Every product we carry, we'd give to our own pack.</p>

    <p>We started this shop because we wanted to do <strong>two things</strong>: bring carefully chosen, genuinely good pet products to other pet parents, and quietly do some good along the way. That's why <strong>1% of every order</strong> goes directly to <a href="https://humanepa.org/donate/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the Humane Society of the Poconos</a>, the same kind of shelter that gave us Jack, Sophie, and Molly.</p>

    <h2>Meet the inspiration</h2>
    <p><strong>Jack</strong> was the first. A scruffy little guy who taught us patience, naps, and how to read a wag.</p>
    <p><strong>Sophie</strong> bounded into our lives next — a fluffy diplomat who thinks every visitor is her best friend.</p>
    <p><strong>Molly</strong> rounded out our pack with pure puppy joy and a reminder of why rescues need our help.</p>

    <blockquote>"Adopting a pet doesn't change the world, but for that one pet, the world changes forever."</blockquote>

    <h2>What we believe in</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Quality over quantity. We only stock products we'd give our own dogs.</li>
      <li>Pets are family. Period.</li>
      <li>Small businesses can do big good.</li>
      <li>Every animal deserves a soft place to land.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Thanks for being here. Thanks for shopping small. And thank you for helping us help the animals still waiting for their forever homes. 🐾</p>
    <p><em>— The Molly &amp; Sophie family</em></p>
  {%- endif -%}
</div>

